"'''Galactic Dance Blast'''" was a [[Jizz/Legends|jizz]] song recorded by [[Evar Orbus and His Galactic Jizz-Wailers]]. Following the death of bandleader [[Evar Orbus/Legends|Evar Orbus]], many of the surviving band members formed the [[Max Rebo Band/Legends|Max Rebo Band]] and continued to perform it.<ref name="Slugthrowers" />

==Behind the scenes==
It is notable for never getting an official release due to its master tape being lost after its usage on the documentary ''[[From Star Wars to Jedi: The Making of a Saga]]''. Some unfinished <!--bootleg?--> versions of the song are on YouTube.<ref name="YouTube">{{YouTube|video=VacG9L2Zkq8|text=Max Rebo - Galactic Dance Blast (remastered)|channel=UCrs7XVV-DiBvfjp-Z_AiPWA|name=Polibot}}</ref> Because the original music is lost, it is not known if these two snippets are from the same song, or if there are two forms of music with the same title.

